@startuml
title Компонентная схема runtime: Telegram Bot ↔ Qmatic Orchestra 6
!include style.iuml
left to right direction
skinparam nodesep 70
skinparam ranksep 70

actor "Посетитель\nTelegram-клиент" as Visitor
cloud "Telegram Cloud" as TelegramCloud {
  component "Telegram Bot API\napi.telegram.org:443" as TelegramApi <<external>>
}

node "Queue Telegram Bot\nmain_bot.py" as BotNode {
  rectangle "Конфигурация\n.env / environment" as Env <<config>>
  component "Aiogram dispatcher\n/start, callbacks, FSM" as Aiogram <<bot>>
  component "BranchConfig loader\nORCHESTRA_BRANCHES + fallback" as BranchLoader <<bot>>
  component "Service menu builder\nGET services + blacklist" as ServiceMenu <<bot>>
  component "Visit creator\nPOST entryPoints/{id}/visits" as VisitCreator <<bot>>
  component "CometD client\nhandshake / subscribe / INIT / connect" as CometDClient <<bot>>
  component "CometD watchdog\nrestart + exponential backoff" as Watchdog <<bot>>
  component "Visit message renderer\nVISIT_CALL_TEMPLATE + override" as MessageRenderer <<bot>>
  queue "USER_BRANCH_SUBSCRIPTIONS\nchat_id -> allowed branch prefixes" as UserBranchMap
}

node "Qmatic Orchestra 6" as OrchestraNode {
  component "REST API\n/services, /visits" as RestApi <<orchestra>>
  component "CometD endpoint\n/cometd, /events/{prefix}/QVoiceLight" as CometDEndpoint <<orchestra>>
  database "Orchestra DB\nvisits, services, queues" as Db
}

Env --> BranchLoader : branches, prefixes, entryPointId, templates
BranchLoader --> Aiogram : branch menu / fallback mode
Aiogram --> ServiceMenu : выбран branchId
ServiceMenu --> RestApi : GET services
Aiogram --> VisitCreator : selected branch + service
VisitCreator --> RestApi : POST visit + TelegramCustomerId
VisitCreator --> UserBranchMap : store chat_id -> branch prefix

CometDClient --> CometDEndpoint : subscribe by all prefixes
CometDEndpoint --> CometDClient : VISIT_CALL event
CometDClient --> UserBranchMap : validate allowed prefix
CometDClient --> MessageRenderer : render branch/global template
MessageRenderer --> TelegramApi : sendMessage(chat_id, text)
Watchdog ..> CometDClient : restart if crashed / no connect

Visitor --> TelegramApi : commands / callbacks
TelegramApi --> Aiogram : polling updates
Aiogram --> TelegramApi : menus / ticket number
RestApi --> Db : read/write
CometDEndpoint --> Db : event source

legend bottom center
|= Зона |= Компоненты |
| Runtime | main_bot.py: polling, FSM, REST calls, CometD, watchdog |
| Конфигурация | branch_config.py: multi-branch JSON + single-branch fallback |
| Уведомления | visit_message.py: safe template rendering for VISIT_CALL |
| Интеграция | Orchestra REST + CometD events, Telegram Bot API |
endlegend
@enduml
